Rlease check-list 
-----------------

* `defaultconfig` under eazytext/__init__.py must be consistent with
  docs/config.etx document. Must also be consistent with pluggdapps-bootstrap
  definition of eazytext config parameters.
* Change the release version in 
    ./CHANGELOG,
    ./eazytext/__init__.py
* Update setup.py and MANIFEST.in for release
* Create a tag and push the tagged branch to launch-pad.
* Upload the source into pypi.
        make upload
